        <updateDate>2020-09-17T20:07:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop PPE Taxes Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill suspends through December 31, 2022, any duty imposed on specified articles and articles identified by the U.S. International Trade Commission as related to the response to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
